><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/university-of-the-witwatersrand-wits-postgraduate-application\/#Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_WITS\" title=\"Applying for Financial Assistance in WITS\">Applying for Financial Assistance in WITS<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80770526\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751340\"><\/a>Contents<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc81153429\">About the University of the Witwatersrand (WITS) Postgraduate Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc81153430\">How to Apply for WITS Postgraduate Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc81153431\">Documents Required for WITS Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc81153432\">WITS Graduate Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc81153433\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc81153434\">Applying for Financial Assistance in WITS<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-university-of-the-witwatersrand-wits-postgraduate-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_University_of_the_Witwatersrand_WITS_Postgraduate_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81153429\"><\/a>About the University of the Witwatersrand (WITS) Postgraduate Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the University of the Witwatersrand (WITS) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigents and International) for admission into <strong>Postgraduate programmes<\/strong> for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p>Before applying, see if they know the programs (Courses) available for the 2024 Postgraduate admission.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply-for-wits-postgraduate-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Apply_for_WITS_Postgraduate_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81153430\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80770527\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751341\"><\/a>How to Apply for WITS Postgraduate Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wits.ac.za\/applications\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Select the <strong>2024 Postgraduate Programmes<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-wits-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_WITS_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81153431\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80770528\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751342\"><\/a>Documents Required for WITS Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>A valid NBT Academic Literacy Test Plus report with an overall Upper Intermediate or above score.<\/li>\n<li>A TOEFL iBT Score Report with an overall score of 88 or above, with at least 19 in Listening, 19 in Writing, 20 in Reading, and 22 in Speaking.<\/li>\n<li>A valid IELTS Academic Test Report Form with an overall score of band 6.5 or above, with at least 6.0 in each component.<\/li>\n<li>A valid PTE Academic Score Report with an overall score of 67 or above, with at least 59 in each communicative skills component.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/self-service.wits.ac.za\/\" class=\"broken_link\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click Here to View more documents<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"wits-graduate-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WITS_Graduate_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81153432\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80770529\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751343\"><\/a>WITS Graduate Application Fees 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a Non-refundable application fee of <strong>R200 <\/strong>for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a Non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of <strong>R200<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Payments are to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<li>Ensure to use your Person Number or T Number as a reference<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81153433\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80770530\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751344\"><\/a>Application Deadline:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>30 September 2024 <\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"applying-for-financial-assistance-in-wits\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_WITS\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc81153434\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80770531\"><\/a><a name=\"_Toc80751345\"><\/a>Applying for Financial Assistance in WITS<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicants can apply for financial assistance (Scholarship) through the NSFAS application <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wits.ac.za\/study-at-wits\/financial-aid-and-scholarships-administration\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">portal<\/a><\/p>\n<p>International students \u2013 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wits.ac.za\/internationalstudents\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click Here<\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wits.ac.za\/applications\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Click here to Apply<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"WITS Postgraduate Application 2024 for Admission into University of the Witwatersrand, WITS Application fees, Programs (Courses), Application Status,&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":18925,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[439],"tags":[66],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1224"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/